  <!-- EN: psychic soothe -->
  <PsychicDrone.stages.psychic_soothe.label>サイコスード</PsychicDrone.stages.psychic_soothe.label>
  <!-- EN: It's like a calming voice at the back of my mind, soothing me, settling my nerves. -->
  <PsychicDrone.stages.psychic_soothe.description>心の内側からする穏やかな声が,私の心の中枢をなだめてくれる.</PsychicDrone.stages.psychic_soothe.description>
  <!-- EN: low psychic drone -->
  <PsychicDrone.stages.low_psychic_drone.label>サイコドローン(低度)</PsychicDrone.stages.low_psychic_drone.label>
  <!-- EN: It's like a scratching at the back of my mind. A voice, whispering. I can only make out a few words, and I don't like them. -->
  <PsychicDrone.stages.low_psychic_drone.description>それは心の内側を爪で引っ掻かれるようなもの. 声,ささやくような声, いくつかの, 私の嫌いな言葉だけ, かろうじて聞き分けられる.</PsychicDrone.stages.low_psychic_drone.description>
  <!-- EN: moderate psychic drone -->
  <PsychicDrone.stages.moderate_psychic_drone.label>サイコドローン(中度)</PsychicDrone.stages.moderate_psychic_drone.label>
  <!-- EN: I feel like someone is always just out of sight, speaking to me. The voice changes but the message doesn't. I'm supposed to hurt people. Make it go away! -->
  <PsychicDrone.stages.moderate_psychic_drone.description>視界の外にいる誰かから,常に話しかけられている気がする.声は変わってもメッセージは変わらない.このままでは,私はそいつを傷つけてしまう,そいつを何処かに追いやって.</PsychicDrone.stages.moderate_psychic_drone.description>
  <!-- EN: high psychic drone -->
  <PsychicDrone.stages.high_psychic_drone.label>サイコドローン(重度)</PsychicDrone.stages.high_psychic_drone.label>
  <!-- EN: The voice is unbearably loud. It's hard to concentrate. I find myself talking back to it, yelling at it. But it just keeps shouting! -->
  <PsychicDrone.stages.high_psychic_drone.description>その声は我慢できない程騒々しい,集中力を維持するのが難しく.そいつに向かって大声で話しかけている自分自身に気がついた.そして,私は大声で叫んでいる.</PsychicDrone.stages.high_psychic_drone.description>
  <!-- EN: extreme psychic drone -->
  <PsychicDrone.stages.extreme_psychic_drone.label>サイコドローン(極度)</PsychicDrone.stages.extreme_psychic_drone.label>
  <!-- EN: My heart pounds and I'm sweating. All I can think of is hurting and suffering and all these enemies around me. They're my nightmare, my nightmare, my nightmare... -->
  <PsychicDrone.stages.extreme_psychic_drone.description>私の心臓はドキドキ鳴り,汗をかいている.私が考えられる全ては,痛み,悩み,そして私の周りにいる悪い奴らの事だ.奴らは,私の悪夢だ…私の悪夢だ…私の悪夢だ….</PsychicDrone.stages.extreme_psychic_drone.description>
  
  <!-- EN: psychic emanator soothe -->
  <PsychicEmanatorSoothe.stages.psychic_emanator_soothe.label>サイコスード波動器</PsychicEmanatorSoothe.stages.psychic_emanator_soothe.label>
  <!-- EN: The psychic emanator makes me feel strange, but also very relaxed. -->
  <PsychicEmanatorSoothe.stages.psychic_emanator_soothe.description>サイコスード波動器は不思議な感覚がして,とてもリラックスさせてくれる.</PsychicEmanatorSoothe.stages.psychic_emanator_soothe.description>
  
  <!-- EN: psychic hangover -->
  <PsychicEntropyHangover.stages.psychic_hangover.label>サイキック酔い</PsychicEntropyHangover.stages.psychic_hangover.label>
  <!-- EN: My body and my eyes ache, but I know it's from my brain. -->
  <PsychicEntropyHangover.stages.psychic_hangover.description>身体と両目が痛い,それが大脳由来だってことも解っている.</PsychicEntropyHangover.stages.psychic_hangover.description>
  
